{"tid":2158812,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"川普之弟Robert Trump病逝享年71歲","createTime":"2020-08-16T02:57:55.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-16T02:57:55.000Z","uid":28765,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"00f9d47aa44c36111a0e0e807ca22f705df2bb29","tid":2158812,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-16T02:57:55.000Z","msg":"即時新聞／綜合報導〕美國總統川普（Donald Trump）發表聲明，證實弟弟（Robert Trump）在當地時間16日晚間病逝，享年71歲。<br />\n<br />\n綜合外媒報導，川普15日才前往紐約長老會醫院（NewYork-Presbyterian Hospital）探望病重的弟弟。川普也在同日的白宮記者會上表示，自己有一名優秀的弟弟，從他出生起，兩人的關係就相當好，更提到希望弟弟的病情盡快好轉.....<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3261802\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3261802&d=Z4osEZd2TI9THLKNWu9EL67%2FPCTF2%2B9SGuy7I2Db2XM%3D&h=79c0b6b5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3261802&h=e1eb3ee1\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3261802</a>"}]}